Invocation Name: name genie
des:
Name Genie is still traveling around the world for names and currently discovered over ten thousand names from the following countries : Austria, Belgium, Canada, Germany, India, Italy, Mexico, Nigeria, Romania, Spain and The United States. 

You can ask for a random name from a certain country or by gender. Name Genie will always look to pull you the best name possible based off your request. If you do not provide a country we will provide names from the United States by default.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
